In today's video, we're investigating the history, and the current activities, of the infamous internet cult "764"... 

This video contains unsettling content. We have included multiple warnings within the video about this fact. Please note that this video complies with all YT and Advertiser guidelines, and the content shown is strictly for documentary and educational purposes. This video is meant to educate the public on one of the greatest online threats facing youth today. The video is also in the public's interest, and falls under Educational, Documentary, Scientific, or Artistic (EDSA) context.

Please note that I have not personally entered any channels or servers related to 764, and thus, I have no first-hand knowledge of their operations. All information presented has been sourced from news outlets, investigative journalism, etc. 

This video was made entirely by humans.
